{"tid":1780382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[I屍A屍]清潔前管工涉偽造值勤紀錄詐騙港鐵 被廉署起訴","createTime":"2019-12-12T10:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:55:37.000Z","uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4efe8909b522422093615bc4b1fe34e47044954e","tid":1780382,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:19:06.000Z","msg":"廉署今日落案起訴一名清潔服務承辦商前管工，控告他涉嫌偽造清潔工值勤紀錄，詐騙香港鐵路有限公司(港鐵公司)服務費用。被告將於下星期一(16日)在西九龍裁判法院答辯。獲廉署准予保釋，以待下星期一應訊。<br />\n<br />\n被告為56歲的吳少平，是永順清潔服務有限公司(永順)前管工，被控一項欺詐罪名。廉署早前接獲貪污投訴，調查後揭發上述涉嫌罪行。<br />\n<br />\n永順於案發時獲港鐵公司聘用為南昌站提供清潔服務。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告涉嫌向港鐵公司偽稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">兩名清潔工分別於2017年3月18日至4月23日期間指定的8日及1日當值，並意圖詐騙而誘使港鐵公司不從永順的清潔服務費用中扣除<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3375</span>元</span>，導致永順獲得利益或港鐵公司蒙受不利。"},{"pid":"8ca34dac6c3ce2caf00811b20363e6a1ed6c6e04","tid":1780382,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"捉魚毛<br />\n真係豐功偉跡"},{"pid":"a4a1ebf76dd52e80ead732a4f6b8c205b079097b","tid":1780382,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46eba36774bcdb6ad36ff1e056d8906bb43a50b0","tid":1780382,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMpfGhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMpfGhq.jpg&h=7797a7f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3601d13fbc4b907f4b67a5740fc4011222e2509f","tid":1780382,"uid":137725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"香港勝在有ICAC<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母"},{"pid":"deb9fbfeb8e7460bf5ac4dcf59c8191d0c397397","tid":1780382,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"icac去左邊？<br />\n<br />\n研訊期間多次揭發記錄警員巡倉的流水簿疑造假，在死者被羈押的12小時內共有18個疑偽造的巡倉紀錄，相關警員分別聲稱肚痛、頭痛或往升旗等，並一律拒回應相關偽造紀錄由誰填寫；另有警員承認以「點名」方式巡倉，僅在門口叫喊疑犯名字當巡倉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181106/20539622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539622&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=2fd4dd33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181106%2F20539622&h=b27e0455\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181106/20539622</a>"},{"pid":"8f498388f7e95381985197ca9fbb1a8a3428515d","tid":1780382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"de4cc30c3ff6b254043acf1d7c66bfe5cd472bb5","tid":1780382,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:28:08.000Z","msg":"家下icac好似變左hr咁, 已經第n單捉員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa94459aabe4d5d03ab9e3bbb6278d551eea336","tid":1780382,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"港共高官、商界高層、慈善總理又唔見ICAC行動，捉魚毛就叻"},{"pid":"94d42c084ea168a8cdbc2077c9c091eeedb059f8","tid":1780382,"uid":27871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tooQmo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tooQmo.jpg&h=effe4e6b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}